16:21.897 --> 16:24.316
Entourage:
Whoa... Hey!

16:24.316 --> 16:26.068
- What was that?
- (distant explosion)

16:26.068 --> 16:28.654
- NoHo Hank: Hm.
- What the fuck was that?

