16:49.591 --> 16:52.636
- (tires squealing)
- (gunfire continues)

16:52.636 --> 16:55.931
- (engine roaring)
- (bullets ricocheting)

16:57.474 --> 17:00.519
- (entourage yelling)
- (windows breaking)

17:00.519 --> 17:03.689
(tires screeching)

17:13.031 --> 17:16.118
(line ringing)

17:16.118 --> 17:18.704
NoHo Hank (on phone):
<i>Oh shit! Call them off!</i>

17:18.704 --> 17:20.956
Fuches:
Why are you shootin'
rockets at my house?

17:20.956 --> 17:22.541
NoHo Hank:
<i>Fucking call them off!</i>

17:22.541 --> 17:24.960
Fuches:
