(grunting, yelping)

17:38.557 --> 17:41.226
<i>Oh God!</i>
(grunts, screams)

17:42.019 --> 17:44.021
(clattering over phone)

17:44.021 --> 17:46.899
(glitching static,
call disconnects)

17:46.899 --> 17:49.985
(muffled TV chatter)

17:49.985 --> 17:51.153
(gasps)

