with Matt and Sean...</i>

19:23.036 --> 19:24.705
(wincing)

19:25.831 --> 19:27.207
(sighs) Fuck.

19:30.419 --> 19:32.546
(wincing)

19:32.546 --> 19:35.716
(TV chatter continues)

19:35.716 --> 19:36.925
(groans)

19:37.843 --> 19:39.595
Oh no.

19:39.595 --> 19:43.098
- (thudding, banging)
- (woozy groan)

19:43.098 --> 19:45.309
(shallow breathing)

19:49.521 --> 19:52.566
- (sighs)
- Announcer (on TV):
<i>Matt, what do you think?</i>

19:52.566 --> 19:53.775
(knocking)

19:53.775 --> 19:56.695
(waves washing ashore,
birds chirping)

19:56.695 --> 19:57.905
(door opens)

19:57.905 --> 20:00.324
Val:
Hello. I believe
my friend is here.

20:00.324 --> 20:03.493
(slight gasp)
Yeah, got him right here.
He's here!

20:03.493 --> 20:06.413
Okay. Thank you, Miss Phoebe,
for letting me use your phone.

20:06.413 --> 20:08.123
- No problem.
- Here. I don't want this.

20:11.376 --> 20:12.753
Hey.

20:12.753 --> 20:13.837
You only gave us one rocket.

20:13.837 --> 20:15.547
You told us
to watch the budget.

20:15.547 --> 20:17.758
Yeah, I was talking
about office supplies.

20:18.467 --> 20:19.801
I see.

20:19.801 --> 20:22.304
This war on Fuches
has entered a new phase.

20:22.304 --> 20:23.805
And what do we
call this phase?

20:23.805 --> 20:27.184
The "give Fuches whatever
he fucking wants" phase.

20:27.184 --> 20:29.227
But Barry can be
anywhere in the world.

20:31.730 --> 20:33.523
♪ ♪

20:33.523 --> 20:36.610
Okay, the acting teacher
