20:36.610 --> 20:38.403
Go to his house.

20:38.403 --> 20:40.155
Put him in a sack.

20:40.155 --> 20:42.407
Bring him to me.

20:42.407 --> 20:44.159
(banging on door)

20:44.159 --> 20:45.702
Sally:
Mr. Cousineau!

20:45.702 --> 20:47.079
(banging)

20:47.079 --> 20:49.456
- Mr. Cousineau! Hello?
- (wind blowing)

20:49.456 --> 20:50.707
(banging)

20:50.707 --> 20:53.919
Fuck!
