would fucking be here.

20:54.419 --> 20:56.672
- Shit.
- (typing on phone)

20:56.672 --> 20:59.716
- When's Dad getting here?
- I don't know, okay?

21:00.550 --> 21:03.720
- John: Can you try
calling him again?
- Look, I...

21:03.720 --> 21:05.305
I just di-- Um...

21:05.305 --> 21:07.015
Mr. Cousineau's
