21:20.487 --> 21:22.197
(panting)

21:24.324 --> 21:27.536
- (sound fades out)
- (shallow breathing)

21:29.246 --> 21:30.747
(inhales)

21:31.498 --> 21:33.208
(exhales)

21:33.458 --> 21:35.377
- (gasps)
- John: Mom?

21:35.377 --> 21:37.713
You look like you're gonna cry.

21:37.713 --> 21:41.174
- (sighs)
- (sound fades in)

21:41.174 --> 21:43.719
- Fuck. (panting)
- (dog barking)

21:43.719 --> 21:46.638
(leaves rustling)

21:46.638 --> 21:50.017
- (distant police radio chatter)
- (dog collar jingling)

21:59.943 --> 22:02.112
You stay here, okay?

22:02.112 --> 22:05.407
(distant police radio
chatter continues)

22:06.158 --> 22:09.286
(nervous breathing)

22:18.170 --> 22:19.421
(quietly)
Hey...

22:19.421 --> 22:22.799
- (dog collar jingling)
- Woman: Okay, take care. Bye.

22:25.260 --> 22:26.636
(pager beeping)

22:29.723 --> 22:31.433
(quietly)
Hey. Hey.

22:32.517 --> 22:35.604
- (radio chatter)
- Hey. Hi. Sir?

22:35.604 --> 22:37.773
(louder)
Sir? Hi. I, um...

22:38.315 --> 22:40.901
Uh, my son?
My son and I.

22:40.901 --> 22:43.070
I, uh, um...

22:43.070 --> 22:44.571
I wanna turn myself in.

22:44.571 --> 22:47.157
Uh, my name is Sally Reed,
and I--

22:47.157 --> 22:48.909
What are you
talking about, ma'am?

22:48.909 --> 22:52.079
(wind blowing)

22:54.039 --> 22:55.165
Uh...

23:00.754 --> 23:02.964
Is there something
you wanna say to me?

23:03.799 --> 23:05.384
No.

23:06.551 --> 23:08.470
Officer:
Alright, well,
have a good day.

23:08.470 --> 23:11.306
(footsteps recede)

23:11.306 --> 23:13.016
(car door opens)

23:13.934 --> 23:15.310
(car door shuts)

23:16.311 --> 23:18.188
- (engine starts)
- (sighs)

23:21.108 --> 23:22.275
John:
Mom!

23:22.275 --> 23:25.195
- Mom! Mom!
- (car driving away)

23:25.195 --> 23:27.280
Is okay. It's okay.

23:27.280 --> 23:30.450
♪ ♪

23:33.787 --> 23:35.163
(shallow breathing)

23:35.163 --> 23:37.415
Oh, Mark is so excited
about this meeting.

23:37.415 --> 23:39.376
Oh, which way...
It's this way.

