23:47.050 --> 23:48.844
- Okay... Okay!
- He doesn't like nervous.

23:48.844 --> 23:50.929
- Mark, it's Matt! (coughs)
- (door creaks)

23:51.471 --> 23:53.932
Hey, Mark,
I have Gene here with me.

23:59.938 --> 24:01.148
(Jim sighs)

24:01.148 --> 24:03.066
You wanna tell us
why Barry Berkman

24:03.066 --> 24:05.986
