for that money.

24:12.200 --> 24:15.996
Why'd you neglect
to mention it to us?

24:15.996 --> 24:17.497
Because no one was
paying attention to me,

24:17.497 --> 24:18.957
and when
you finally did, well,

24:18.957 --> 24:21.293
I had already spent,
like, some of it.

24:24.296 --> 24:26.464
Y-You have no idea
the tension that I was in.

24:26.464 --> 24:29.342
The stress I was feeling.
H-He threw me in a trunk!

24:29.342 --> 24:31.928
