give me a straight answer
about the cash.

24:44.065 --> 24:45.609
Jim:
You changed your story.

24:46.443 --> 24:48.653
Why are you telling
everyone that Barry is a...

24:48.653 --> 24:51.698
sympathetic soul?

24:51.698 --> 24:53.825
I would never say
something like that.

24:53.825 --> 24:56.995
That's not what you
told me. (scoffs)

24:56.995 --> 24:58.455
Who the fuck are you?

24:58.455 --> 25:00.749
Sorry. (laughs) I'm Brad.
I'm an actor.

25:00.749 --> 25:03.543
Um, I was actually in your
Shakespeare class in 2004.

25:03.543 --> 25:06.546
I did a scene from, uh,
"The Merry Wives of Windsor--"

25:06.546 --> 25:10.383
Detective Moss
